				<td><strong>The Value of Planning for Infinite-Horizon Model Predictive Control.</strong> (48% Acceptance Rate)
            <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Hatch21A','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/Hatch21A'); ">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Hatch21A','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>] 
