				<td><strong>Combining pretrained CNN feature extractors to enhance clustering of complex natural images.</strong> 
            <p class="infolinks">[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Guerin20','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/Guerin20'); ">Abstract</a>] [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Guerin20','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>] 
