            <td><strong>Closing the Learning-Planning Loop with Predictive State Representations.</strong> (Invited Journal Paper)
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots11b','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/IJRR11'); ">Abstract</a>]
