				<td><strong>Predictive State Decoders: Encoding the Future into Recurrent Networks.</strong>
            <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Venkatraman17b','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/PSDs_NIPSWS'); ">Abstract</a>]
			[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Venkatraman17b','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>] [<a href="files/PSDs.pdf" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/downloads/NIPSWorkshop2017-PSDs'); ">PDF</a>]
