            <td><strong>Prediction under Uncertainty in Sparse Spectrum Gaussian Processes with Applications to Filtering and Control.</strong>
<p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Pan17a','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/rldm_ssgp'); ">Abstract</a>]
[<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Pan17a','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]
