          <tr id="Boots14NIPSb" class="entry">
            <td> Z. Marinho, A. Dragan, A. Byravan, S. Srinivasa, G. Gordon, &amp; <strong>B. Boots</strong>.</td>
            <td><strong>Functional Gradient Motion Planning in Reproducing Kernel Hilbert Spaces</strong>.
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots14NIPSb','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/NIPSworkshop14b'); ">Abstract</a>]
                [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots14NIPSb','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]
