            D. Fox.</td>
            <td><strong>Layered Hybrid Inverse Optimal Control for Learning Robot Manipulation from Demonstration</strong>.
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots14NIPSd','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/NIPSworkshop13a'); ">Abstract</a>]
                [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots14NIPSd','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]
