            <td><strong>Learning Dynamic Policies from Demonstration</strong>.
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots13NIPSb','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/NIPSworkshop13b'); ">Abstract</a>]
                [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots13NIPSb','bibtex')">BibTeX</a>]
