            <td><strong>Incremental Sparse GP Regression for Continuous-time Trajectory Estimation &amp; Mapping</strong>.
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Yan15arxiv','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/Yan15arxiv'); ">Abstract</a>]
