          <tr id="Boots09arxiv" class="entry">
            <td><strong>B. Boots</strong>,  S. M. Siddiqi &amp; G. J. Gordon.</td>
            <td><strong>Closing the Learning-Planning Loop with Predictive State Representations.</strong> (Updated: 2010)
              <p class="infolinks"> [<a href="javascript:toggleInfo('Boots09arxiv','abstract')" onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/abstracts/arxivPSR'); ">Abstract</a>]
